Mudit Marwaha
Local Guide 29 reviews
a week ago
New
Very nice atmosphere and a variety of shops and restaurants for you to enjoy. Very nice central location and a happening place whenever you go there. There are shops for all sorts of price groups, from budget to high end brands. There are maps everywhere that help make navigating the mall much easier.
Response from the owner a week ago
Mudit, thank you for your glowing 5-star review. We are glad you enjoyed the variety of shops and restaurants that the center has to offer. We hope you visit again soon!
